snippet.title: Plants vs Zombies 1 in 3D  | Unreal Engine 5 Fan Concept
snippet.description:
Watch how I made this here: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9pgvl3lQqcQ&ab_channel=BobbyIvar
Download here for free (PC ONLY): https://bobby-ivar.itch.io/foliage-vs-undead

This is a fan project I made using Unreal Engine 5. I love pvz 1 and wanted to see how it would look reimagined in 3D so I made this small demo.
